707052f-b.title: Brooklyn: Tiffany Pl. - Kane St.
707052f-b.text:
(1)
2-4 Tiffany Place, at the S.W. corner of Kane Street. Also
seen is 105-109 Eane Strect, north side, between Columbia and Hicks
Streets, at the foot of Tiffany Plaoe.
August 5, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)  The same, showing side of No. 4 Tiffany Place and lot, adjoining
the house to the south.
August 5, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
